# Generation 11: binary relations — assert and query relations between things.
> tom is the parent of bob
< Learned: parent(tom, bob).
> is tom the parent of bob?
< Yes.
# Relations are directional.
> is bob the parent of tom?
< No.
> bob is the parent of ann
< Learned: parent(bob, ann).
# Variable query on either position.
> who is the parent of ann?
< bob.
> who is the parent of bob?
< tom.
# Unknown relation -> graceful.
> who is the parent of zara?
< Nobody that I know of.
